Memo

00:00:10.210 --> 00:00:12.320
Good morning.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.330
This is Kosaku Kawajiri.

00:00:14.330 --> 00:00:16.410
I realize this is selfish of me,

00:00:16.410 --> 00:00:19.330
but I will be around fifteen 
minutes late to the office.

00:00:20.120 --> 00:00:25.080
Yes. I have to discipline 
my unreasonable son.

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:31.090
Yes, sir. I realize this would sound 
highly trivial to anyone else. Yes.

00:00:31.090 --> 00:00:33.370
I am terribly sorry.

00:00:33.370 --> 00:00:35.530
Yes, as soon as I'm done.

00:00:35.530 --> 00:00:39.970
Yes, I'll head right to the office.

00:00:39.970 --> 00:00:41.100
Yes.

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:44.100
Yes. If you'll excuse me, sir.

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:52.340
Curse that Kosaku Kawajiri 
being so apologetic.

00:00:52.340 --> 00:00:54.730
Did you want to climb the 
corporate ladder that badly,

00:00:54.730 --> 00:00:56.820
despite how anxious you were?

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.910
The reason Josuke went into that house

00:01:03.910 --> 00:01:09.420
is because he knew he'd have the upper 
hand in a close-quarters battle.

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:12.920
I will admit that's true.

00:01:13.390 --> 00:01:18.620
It's best that I avoid close-quarters 
combat with Shining Diamond.

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:21.460
If I can figure out just where Josuke is,

00:01:21.460 --> 00:01:26.240
I can shoot an air bullet from here, but...

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:28.820
Hey, you.

00:01:29.950 --> 00:01:32.940
What do you think you're 
doing on this property?

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:39.570
What? Are you saying you're 
not on this property?

00:01:39.570 --> 00:01:43.210
Don't get nitpicky with me, 
Mr. Goody Two-shoes.

00:01:43.210 --> 00:01:44.700
Is this your house?

00:01:44.700 --> 00:01:46.320
How long have you been watching?

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:49.580
Hey, I'm the one asking the questions here.

00:01:49.580 --> 00:01:51.130
I live next door.

00:01:51.130 --> 00:01:53.660
I was thinking about sleeping past noon

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:56.330
when I was woken up by some kind of noise.

00:01:56.330 --> 00:01:57.970
You make me suspicious.

00:01:57.970 --> 00:02:02.080
Rio, from next door, said her 
underwear gets stolen all the time.

00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:04.990
And since everyone's 
gone around this time...

00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:06.660
I'm envious...

00:02:06.660 --> 00:02:07.690
Huh?

00:02:07.690 --> 00:02:09.520
Of all the free time you seem to have.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.980
Hey, are you running away?

00:02:11.380 --> 00:02:15.070
Damn him... Going after Rio like that.

00:02:15.070 --> 00:02:17.090
Pisses me off!

00:02:23.300 --> 00:02:25.860
He was an underwear thief after all!

00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:27.910
These panties...

00:02:38.760 --> 00:02:41.800
Th-They're Rio's...

00:02:46.780 --> 00:02:48.520
P-P-Pan...

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:53.690
Woohoo! I'm so lucky!

00:03:09.290 --> 00:03:10.530
Diamond is Unbreakable

00:03:09.290 --> 00:03:10.530
Jojo's Bizarre Adventure

00:04:18.460 --> 00:04:24.100
Episode 38   Shining D (Diamond) is Unbreakable, Part 2

00:04:26.690 --> 00:04:30.080
I-It's no use! The phone line's been cut!

00:04:39.700 --> 00:04:41.660
Okuyasu is dead...

00:04:43.670 --> 00:04:45.780
I'm going to beat the crap out of

00:04:45.780 --> 00:04:50.000
Yoshikage Kira with my Shining 
Diamond and defeat him.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.930
I'm going to end this within a few minutes.

00:04:54.830 --> 00:05:00.440
Hayato, stay along the wall there 
so that Kira can't see you.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.950
Where is he...

00:05:11.670 --> 00:05:14.340
going to enter from... is the question.

00:05:36.900 --> 00:05:37.980
Huh?!

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:41.880
Wh-What?

00:05:42.430 --> 00:05:44.440
J-Josuke!

00:05:45.690 --> 00:05:46.900
It's an air bullet!

00:05:46.900 --> 00:05:48.990
There's one heading toward you right now!

00:05:48.990 --> 00:05:51.600
It's about the same size as earlier...

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.620
B-But that's impossible!

00:05:53.620 --> 00:05:57.120
There's no way he can tell 
where you are from outside!

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.370
How does he know?!

00:06:00.530 --> 00:06:02.130
Great...

00:06:02.780 --> 00:06:05.910
I know, Josuke Higashikata...

00:06:05.910 --> 00:06:07.430
I know the exact distance.

00:06:07.430 --> 00:06:11.180
Three meters until impact...

00:06:17.470 --> 00:06:19.560
I... I can tell...

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:22.700
We can tell where the ball of air is.

00:06:22.700 --> 00:06:23.650
Yes!

00:06:23.650 --> 00:06:25.150
You'll be able to dodge it!

00:06:25.150 --> 00:06:29.620
No matter how many come through, 
you'll be able to dodge them... now...

00:06:31.450 --> 00:06:33.220
What?

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:35.870
I-It's going after Josuke?

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:47.260
Yoshikage Kira knows where I am.

00:06:47.260 --> 00:06:50.260
Where is he? How is he seeing me?

00:06:51.830 --> 00:06:54.170
There were no windows in that room!

00:06:54.170 --> 00:06:55.990
The curtains are all drawn, too!

00:06:55.990 --> 00:06:58.380
There's no way he can see you from outside!

00:06:58.380 --> 00:07:01.740
It's automatic! It must be 
automatically chasing you!

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:04.160
No, that's not right.

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:06.360
The version of Deadly Queen that's

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:09.350
automatic goes after heat 
and is called Heart Attack.

00:07:09.350 --> 00:07:13.160
But... It's not going after 
the lit cigarette there.

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:16.060
More importantly, if it was 
automatically tracking me,

00:07:16.060 --> 00:07:18.920
the air bullet wouldn't be 
able to go through the wall,

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:24.790
and Yoshikage Kira plans to do the final 
detonation himself to finish me off.

00:07:24.790 --> 00:07:29.050
It's a mystery, but he knows exactly where I am!

00:07:29.050 --> 00:07:30.300
It's getting faster!

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.980
Find Kira for me!

00:07:31.980 --> 00:07:34.900
Find out how he's watching me!

00:07:35.900 --> 00:07:37.350
I-I found him!

00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:40.330
H-He's right outside the gate.

00:07:41.610 --> 00:07:44.610
Two meters until impact...

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:46.860
He's outside?

00:07:47.220 --> 00:07:51.570
I can't figure out how he's able to 
pinpoint your location from there, Josuke.

00:07:51.570 --> 00:07:52.950
Hurry and run!

00:07:53.330 --> 00:07:56.950
That bastard! I don't know 
how he's watching me...

00:07:56.950 --> 00:07:58.700
One more meter!

00:07:58.700 --> 00:08:03.460
But I didn't want you chasing 
me in the first place!

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.790
Shining Diamond!

00:08:06.890 --> 00:08:08.710
All right, it's going to impact on Josuke!

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:10.460
Detonate!

00:08:15.050 --> 00:08:17.930
Yes! It was a direct hit!

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:20.220
Deadly Queen!

00:08:21.180 --> 00:08:23.980
My, my, that was close.

00:08:23.980 --> 00:08:26.620
But I was on my guard.

00:08:26.620 --> 00:08:31.170
Your willpower to try to 
get one final blow in...

00:08:31.170 --> 00:08:35.810
That's why I won't go near 
you, Josuke Higashikata.

00:08:35.810 --> 00:08:38.440
J-Josuke!

00:08:40.210 --> 00:08:42.410
H-He's alive...

00:08:42.410 --> 00:08:46.270
Hmph. It was a direct hit, 
but he wasn't blown away.

00:08:46.270 --> 00:08:49.610
There's a slight discrepancy 
when I detonate by hand...

00:08:49.610 --> 00:08:52.340
But the damage is absolute.

00:08:52.710 --> 00:08:55.760
I can finish him off with the next shot!

00:08:57.470 --> 00:09:02.570
W-We... We have to get away from here!

00:09:02.570 --> 00:09:05.410
Y-You're pulling me the wrong way...

00:09:05.410 --> 00:09:08.850
This is the opposite direction...

00:09:08.850 --> 00:09:11.950
Not that way... It's the opposite direction!

00:09:11.950 --> 00:09:14.640
I'm going to kill him!

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:17.530
We need to go in the direction 
of Yoshikage Kira...

00:09:18.460 --> 00:09:21.080
My Shining Diamond

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:23.440
can't fix my own wounds...

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:29.320
But once my blood has left my body and 
hardened, it's just another object.

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:31.720
It's no longer part of me.

00:09:32.370 --> 00:09:35.340
Therefore, I can gather it and 
stick it onto other things.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:39.620
So I stuck some inside a shard of glass.

00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:45.230
The rain stopped, and the blood 
stain on his jacket earlier...

00:09:45.230 --> 00:09:48.060
should have hardened by now!

00:09:48.060 --> 00:09:51.190
That's my automatic tracking bomb.

