00:09:59.660 --> 00:09:59.780
Josuke

00:09:59.780 --> 00:09:59.910
Josuke Higashi

00:09:59.910 --> 00:10:00.950
Josuke Higashikata

00:10:05.100 --> 00:10:09.460
The shard of glass that I was 
able to guard against...

00:10:09.460 --> 00:10:12.480
It must be this blood stain...

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:16.470
This stain must have led that 
glass shard right to me!

00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:18.990
I-It was a direct hit!

00:10:18.990 --> 00:10:21.490
It's embedded right into Kira's back!

00:10:26.680 --> 00:10:28.400
That's...

00:10:30.710 --> 00:10:36.570
Josuke Higashikata's Shining Diamond is 
a Stand whose actions I can't foresee...

00:10:36.570 --> 00:10:40.490
But the damage Josuke sustained 
is greater than mine.

00:10:40.490 --> 00:10:42.170
Just one more shot!

00:10:42.170 --> 00:10:46.830
One more shot and I, 
Yoshikage Kira, will be victorious!

00:10:52.400 --> 00:10:56.960
I-It's here! Th-This one's big enough to see!

00:10:56.960 --> 00:10:58.840
That must mean...

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:01.440
that this is his final shot.

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:04.600
This will be mine, too!

00:11:05.850 --> 00:11:10.050
I-I don't think the same attack 
will work twice on Kira!

00:11:10.050 --> 00:11:10.980
He'll dodge it!

00:11:10.980 --> 00:11:15.600
We'll just have to see about that...

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:18.070
By the way, Hayato, sorry,

00:11:18.070 --> 00:11:21.550
but the lighter from earlier is in my pocket.

00:11:21.550 --> 00:11:23.340
Could you get it for me?

00:11:23.340 --> 00:11:26.200
It's a bit hard for me 
to get it myself with

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:28.700
this pole sticking out of my stomach.

00:11:28.700 --> 00:11:30.730
The smoke is useless now!

00:11:30.730 --> 00:11:32.370
You can see the air bullet!

00:11:32.370 --> 00:11:36.630
The air bullet isn't what I want to 
use the lighter to see this time.

00:11:36.630 --> 00:11:40.520
I'm going to look at something else... So...

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:48.270
Let's find out why he can see where I am.

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:50.390
Don't move, Hayato.

00:11:51.020 --> 00:11:54.120
J-Josuke? Wh-What are you...

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.480
Stay still, Hayato.

00:11:56.990 --> 00:12:00.280
He might not be watching...

00:12:00.280 --> 00:12:02.910
He might be listening.

00:12:03.860 --> 00:12:06.610
Kira had a cell phone.

00:12:06.610 --> 00:12:09.040
Did he just happen to have it? No!

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:11.600
So then, who was he talking to?

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:14.290
Was it his boss from the office? 
No, that's not right.

00:12:14.290 --> 00:12:18.960
There's only one person that Kira 
would be calling right now...

00:12:27.970 --> 00:12:32.490
I'd completely forgotten about you, 
old man in the picture...

00:12:32.490 --> 00:12:37.230
The one who's trying to 
protect Yoshikage Kira!

00:12:37.230 --> 00:12:41.650
I have no idea when he got 
inside my pocket, but...

00:12:41.650 --> 00:12:45.110
So this was the answer!

00:12:46.770 --> 00:12:50.160
Th-The air bullet passed through the window!

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:51.540
Get back!

00:12:55.820 --> 00:12:57.170
It impacted!

00:12:57.170 --> 00:13:01.720
Josuke... is running away three meters ahead.

00:13:03.900 --> 00:13:06.990
Sh-Shit!

00:13:06.990 --> 00:13:08.930
I-It passed him!

00:13:08.930 --> 00:13:14.010
And he's now moving diagonally 
right, then up... Three meters.

00:13:15.770 --> 00:13:19.770
He hasn't figured out that it's Josuke 
because he's using a raspy voice!

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:26.110
And now, he's running away 
one meter to the left...

00:13:26.110 --> 00:13:30.590
What?! How can you do that, you bastard?!

00:13:30.590 --> 00:13:32.620
Right there. Detonate!

00:13:33.500 --> 00:13:36.790
Yoshikage!

00:13:46.580 --> 00:13:49.950
I did it! Josuke's been 
blown away, hasn't he?

00:13:49.950 --> 00:13:52.170
Yeah, he was gloriously blown away.

00:13:52.750 --> 00:13:55.760
All the way to Hell, with my directions.

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:58.540
Though, I mean, he was 
a ghost to begin with,

00:13:58.540 --> 00:14:01.060
so it's more like he finally made it over.

00:14:01.060 --> 00:14:02.610
Josuke...

00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:08.490
J-Josuke!

00:14:10.650 --> 00:14:16.210
Th-This must be some kind of mistake...

00:14:16.210 --> 00:14:19.220
Something this horrible...

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:26.220
should not be happening in my life...

00:14:26.220 --> 00:14:31.970
when I just want to live 
as peacefully as a plant...

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:37.970
But what I mustn't forget 
at times like these

00:14:37.970 --> 00:14:40.210
is that it's in times like these,

00:14:40.210 --> 00:14:41.980
horrible times like these,

00:14:42.290 --> 00:14:44.980
that opportunities present themselves.

00:14:44.980 --> 00:14:47.090
I've learned that in the past.

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:51.540
When I'm backed into a corner, 
if I think things through rationally,

00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:54.200
opportunities will make 
themselves available!

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:58.650
I, Yoshikage Kira, have always done this.

00:14:58.650 --> 00:15:02.480
There is no trouble that I was

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.440
unable to overcome...

00:15:04.940 --> 00:15:06.710
Ever!

00:15:15.550 --> 00:15:19.390
You're within my range...

00:15:19.390 --> 00:15:21.760
Yoshikage Kira!

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:31.620
H-He's near him!

00:15:31.620 --> 00:15:34.990
H-He finally got near him!

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:39.530
This is a close-quarters match, 
and it'll be over in an instant.

00:15:39.530 --> 00:15:42.130
Josuke's ability is greater,

00:15:42.130 --> 00:15:45.750
b-but if Kira touches him,
he'll be turned into a bomb!

00:15:45.750 --> 00:15:51.630
A-And the wounds in Josuke's 
leg and torso from that blast...

00:15:51.630 --> 00:15:56.310
Josuke, you shouldn't even 
be able to stand right now.

00:15:56.310 --> 00:15:59.810
Josuke Higashikata!

00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:05.610
Bring out... your Deadly Queen...

00:16:22.460 --> 00:16:23.830
Deadly Queen!

00:16:38.850 --> 00:16:40.310
H-He's strong...

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:43.820
I'm going to be defeated...

00:16:43.820 --> 00:16:46.190
I, Yoshikage Kira, am going to be defeated!

00:16:52.370 --> 00:16:55.680
N-No... How could...

00:16:55.680 --> 00:16:59.700
We were so close! 
Josuke is stronger than him!

00:16:59.700 --> 00:17:04.460
Is fate really on the side of that murderer?

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:10.250
M-My fists didn't hit him...

00:17:10.810 --> 00:17:13.580
These air bullets acted like cushions!

00:17:13.580 --> 00:17:18.040
B-But it wasn't my intention 
to have it guard me...

00:17:18.040 --> 00:17:19.850
I didn't have time for that!

00:17:21.580 --> 00:17:23.020
Stray Cat!

00:17:23.300 --> 00:17:27.800
I see... Stray Cat thought 
it was being attacked,

00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:30.020
so it instinctively blocked the attack!

00:17:30.390 --> 00:17:33.600
This is my chance! This is that chance!

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:36.660
A opportunity has presented itself 
at the worst of times, after all!

00:17:36.660 --> 00:17:38.340
Deadly Queen!

00:17:38.340 --> 00:17:41.240
Change that air bullet into a bomb!

00:17:43.150 --> 00:17:44.160
I've won!

00:17:44.570 --> 00:17:46.390
I've changed it into a contact bomb!

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:49.130
It'll explode if anyone touches it.

00:17:49.130 --> 00:17:52.330
Josuke, with the damage you're 
currently suffering from,

00:17:52.330 --> 00:17:55.920
you won't have the strength to dodge this!

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:59.010
Yoshikage Kira!

00:17:59.010 --> 00:18:01.180
It's a contact bomb?!

00:18:01.180 --> 00:18:04.910
Josuke! It doesn't matter 
if it's glass or wood!

00:18:04.910 --> 00:18:07.040
Hit that and take cover!

00:18:08.540 --> 00:18:14.030
I've won! This always happens 
when life deals its worst to me!

00:18:14.030 --> 00:18:17.780
Luck is on the side of Yoshikage Kira!

00:18:23.650 --> 00:18:25.450
Wh-What?!

00:18:25.450 --> 00:18:29.920
Th-The air bullet went off its course!

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:34.090
Y-You're...

00:18:34.090 --> 00:18:35.460
You're...

00:18:36.180 --> 00:18:37.970
You're...

00:18:38.710 --> 00:18:41.470
O-Okuyasu!

00:18:41.470 --> 00:18:45.100
You know, I always wonder

00:18:45.100 --> 00:18:50.980
where all the stuff I scrape 
away with The Hand goes.

00:18:50.980 --> 00:18:53.260
Though I'm not really smart,

00:18:53.260 --> 00:18:56.320
so whenever I think too much 
about anything, I get a headache.

00:18:56.320 --> 00:18:57.130
There.

00:18:57.130 --> 00:18:58.570
What?!

00:18:58.570 --> 00:19:02.660
I-I can't believe it... I-It's Okuyasu.

00:19:02.660 --> 00:19:06.530
But his heart and breathing 
had completely stopped...

00:19:07.190 --> 00:19:10.330
I had a weird dream...

00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:18.220
While I was walking amid the darkness 
in that dream, I saw a light.

00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:25.010
And I saw my dead brother...

00:19:26.460 --> 00:19:29.140
My big brother, Keicho.

00:19:29.940 --> 00:19:33.400
He asked me where I was going,

00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:37.400
so I said that I was going to follow him.

00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:41.530
I mean, my Bro was always reliable.

00:19:41.530 --> 00:19:45.410
He never made any bad decisions, 
so I'd have nothing to worry about.

00:19:45.880 --> 00:19:50.870
But then he said I should decide for myself.

00:19:50.870 --> 00:19:55.600
He said, "Okuyasu, you're the one who 
has to decide where you're going to go."

00:19:57.980 --> 00:20:00.670
I thought for a bit,

00:20:00.670 --> 00:20:05.370
and answered that I was going back 
to Morioh, and then I woke up.

00:20:05.980 --> 00:20:08.760
It was a really sad dream.

00:20:09.410 --> 00:20:11.440
Okuyasu...

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:17.270
Y-You've got some nerve, 
dreaming at a time like this!

00:20:18.070 --> 00:20:22.000
There's that lousy attitude! 
Despite your wounds,

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:24.500
you seem pretty okay.

00:20:25.620 --> 00:20:27.020
Shut up!

00:20:27.020 --> 00:20:30.790
If you were alive, you should 
have woken up sooner, damn it!

00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:37.830
I-Impossible... Fate should 
have been on my side...

00:20:37.830 --> 00:20:40.800
I should have been given my opportunity!

00:20:42.090 --> 00:20:45.050
Stray Cat! Shoot another shot!

00:20:50.640 --> 00:20:52.390
Wh-What?!

00:20:52.390 --> 00:20:54.400
Wh-Wh-Whoa... Whoa, there.

00:20:54.400 --> 00:21:00.900
Y-Yes! Now Kira won't be able 
to use his air bullet bombs!

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:07.100
Th-Th-There's...

00:21:09.490 --> 00:21:15.140
There has never been any trouble that I, 
Yoshikage Kira, was unable to overcome!

00:21:15.140 --> 00:21:17.380
Look, Jotaro!

00:21:17.380 --> 00:21:20.480
That loud sound must've 
come from that house.

00:21:20.480 --> 00:21:23.130
I wonder what happened. Was it a gas explosion?

00:21:23.890 --> 00:21:27.640
L-Look! That man is injured!

00:21:42.690 --> 00:21:45.290
Josuke and Okuyasu are there, too!

00:21:45.290 --> 00:21:48.200
That kid is Hayato Kawajiri from the picture.

00:21:48.200 --> 00:21:51.670
And that man is Kosaku Kawajiri.

00:21:51.670 --> 00:21:54.410
It looks like everything's falling into place.

00:21:57.460 --> 00:22:00.500
Any fate that would side with you...

00:22:00.500 --> 00:22:03.500
Any opportunity that would come your way...

00:22:03.500 --> 00:22:09.180
is nothing compared to the heart 
of justice that's here right now!

00:22:09.970 --> 00:22:14.480
It's definitely here! It's right here for sure!

00:22:14.480 --> 00:22:16.990
Compared to that heart, you're nothing!

